            "relationship": "REQUIRES",
            "direction": "cfg_strength -> drop_audio_cond",
            "description": "cfg_strength > 0 triggers a dual forward pass inside CFM.sample. The null (unconditioned) prediction uses drop_audio_cond=True internally. cfg_strength cannot function without this routing."
